modShortDescription: Adds cosmetic boots mods to the game. Work the same as the cowboy hat and ball cap mods. Craftable with the boots of your choice and a sewing kit.
modDescription:
Adds cosmetic boots mods to the game. Work the same as the cowboy hat and ball cap mods. Craftable with the [boots](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-clothing/) of your choice and a sewing kit. Does not include hazmat.

**[Download](https://docs.google.com/uc?export=download&id=1LnoaspE71qtBjAsqtiGvzwiMCgZ6gsHb)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/20895-toads-modlets/).

**Credits:** [AnsontheToad](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/ansonthetoad/)
